# KitchCu Frontend Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/KITCHCU-ENGINEERING-STANDARDS.md` first.

## Stack (Phase 1 — current)

- React 18 + Vite + TypeScript + React Router 7
- Tailwind + project CSS (`apps/website/src/index.css`)
- Brand/hosts: `apps/website/src/shared/brand.ts` (single source)
- Cross-app URLs: `apps/website/src/shared/urls.ts`

## Apps (`apps/website/`)

| App | Host | Port |
|-----|------|------|
| Portal | kitchcu.in | 13000 |
| Customer | customer.kitchcu.in | 13001 |
| Kitchen | kitchen.kitchcu.in | 13002 |
| Admin | admin.kitchcu.in | 13003 |

Build: `npm run build:portal|customer|kitchen|admin`

## API

- Gateway only: `/api/v1/` — never call services directly
- Owner JWT in kitchen app · isolated from customer session keys

## UX (cloud kitchen only)

- Owner: inbox-first · one primary action per screen
- Customer: discovery-first · trust via live-capture media
- Minimum touch target 44px · hi/en i18n (Phase 2)

## Dish photos

- Hero: live-capture required (`is_live_capture: true`)
- Server rejects stock-photo heroes

## Phase 2 targets (ADR before adoption)

TanStack Query · React Hook Form · Workbox PWA offline · push notifications

## Do not

- Hardcode subdomains — use `brand.ts` constants
- Build native apps before PWA stable
- Add restaurant POS / dine-in UI patterns
